=== Spec Example 8.21. Block Scalar Nodes
from: http://www.yaml.org/spec/1.2/spec.html#id2799693
tags: spec literal folded 1.3-err

+++ in-yaml
literal: |2
  value
folded:
   !foo
  >1
 value

+++ in-json
{
  "folded": "value\n",
  "literal": "value\n"
}

+++ out-yaml
literal: |
  value
folded: !foo >
  value

+++ test-event
+STR
+DOC
+MAP
=VAL :literal
=VAL |value\n
=VAL :folded
=VAL <!foo> >value\n
-MAP
-DOC
-STR
